Wally Wales https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wally_Wales 0 Wally Wales (born Floyd Taliaferro Alderson, November 13, 1895 – February 10, 1980) was an American film actor who also appeared in many films under the name Hal Taliaferro. He appeared in more than 220 films between 1921 and 1964.
